parent":"127","text":"T1 con gadolinio → tumores, abscesos","guid":"K4hn7SXvR3aGvFs-7q_Y-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"Angio-TC/RM → patología vascular","guid":"bh2EeB1STdKBopgXC42Jrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"124","text":"Pruebas estandarizadas de lenguaje","guid":"6sT8pW9OTZGPtwZ_zC2qzg","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Test de Boston (BDAE)","guid":"BjFnJk_hQF2Sun84IHnZLQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Western Aphasia Battery (WAB)","guid":"WuGuNVKaRWKd-ESBQpnIhQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"Token Test → comprensión","guid":"X0zrasGPR--Oca6a7IJXkw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"Fluencia verbal fonémica (FAS) y semántica (animales)","guid":"Ast54AhrQZqVPWjpaVnVxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"124","text":"Evaluación fonoaudiológica → Frenchay Dysarthria Assessment","guid":"d6ISVXiORjadctbvT6iSyg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"124","text":"EEG → si sospecha crisis epiléptica (afasia ictal)","guid":"yxfEDKHeS3aw0g51bOuBsw","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"124","text":"EMG/VCN → si sospecha miastenia o neuropatía","guid":"jI76mKdJQrK667cYNpCazg","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones Geriátricas","guid":"LPB8q8FmSemTjZWWnbxG-g","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Afasia en AM → SIEMPRE descartar ACV primero","guid":"oqfUH_qnR9iSLKPioDpDgw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Afasia progresiva → APP (afasia primaria progresiva)","guid":"Niychj1LQJa8omeKBua3Uw","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Variante no fluente/agramática → degeneración frontal","guid":"MaYsCRVpQv28khaJp7pPXA","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Variante semántica → atrofia temporal anterior","guid":"P_5w93d9RvyMwvJ2EK884Q","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Variante logopénica → Alzheimer atípico","guid":"MgX_uo8dRsWm06QrFOHlUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"140","text":"Disartria en AM → causas más frecuentes","guid":"a7mN98frSraPXFIs0cb70A","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"ACV (más común)","guid":"cYGbg9EvRICGGYFfXwok0g","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Parkinsonismo","guid":"cQf9-EZETtOr09LguNuyWQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"ELA (inicio bulbar → disartria + disfagia)","guid":"7tJZK92rQBOUc1OPA62deA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"146","text":"Polifarmacia → BZD, antiepilépticos, antipsicóticos","guid":"5bcKp9DXQCakDdVoqPlDTg","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"140","text":"Prótesis dental desajustada → SIMULA o EXACERBA disartria","guid":"SeKXEWATSt-A5FyBWPIEng","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Evaluar ajuste protésico SIEMPRE antes de tratar","guid":"iajTZbBDRTu45GQJjgR9LQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"140","text":"Presbifagia + disartria → evaluar riesgo aspiración","guid":"S-WTHBJiRhSVsFN_S3YJMw","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"Voz húmeda post-ingesta → asumir aspiración silente","guid":"N3R7nesfT6OPRU2_2F_cKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"140","text":"Delirium → alteración lenguaje fluctuante NO es afasia","guid":"lsRjxS5xQz-neKf9mxx-8w","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"140","text":"Hipoacusia → descartar ANTES de evaluar comprensión","guid":"FQ5npE1YTNe9iSk7JCPyWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"9guoZ-dATT6bCX2OkfQ9JA","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Escritura preservada + comprensión intacta = DISARTRIA, no afasia","guid":"wdBiPqnvQ0C0K2wznb5DPw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Afasias PERISILVIANAS alteran la repetición → regla de oro","guid":"t8DWZ2qFTfyPfBzQkuftSA","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Habla escándida (scanning) = CEREBELO hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"60zJOnivTgSbAA5u0QuGhw","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"Disartria espástica + flácida combinadas = pensar ELA","guid":"mLfFqLNlTaGPsi01pz_F5A","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"Prótesis dental desajustada simula disartria → revisar SIEMPRE en AM","guid":"nBQ4nMGOQWq8hCGKSSpVyw","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"Afasia progresiva en AM → variante logopénica orienta a Alzheimer","guid":"19NMUTr8TdqEn9Fb6WEHDw","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"157","text":"Voz húmeda post-ingesta en disártrico → aspiración silente, EMST protector","guid":"8t2VvkxSQxOQYG5mCilAuA","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"157","text":"Disartria hipocinética + micrografía → Parkinson","guid":"YBDG3amySj6RWCW3aPIpbA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"157","text":"Anosognosia del déficit → típico de Wernicke (no reconoce su error)","guid":"Nx7aG1GtQs2fSxCufHW9Bw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"157","text":"Afasia ictal (crisis epiléptica) → transitoria, EEG diagnóstico","guid":"0BYfTmiMSq2YOXqp_hHcrQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"157","text":"Dominancia hemisférica izquierda en >95% diestros → lesión izq = afasia","guid":"rQ2R3YE-RG2mqVv62N7EQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"slf3Fw4WTNqGVLG_OrEjHQ","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"1. Duffy JR. Motor Speech Disorders: Substrates, Differential Diagnosis, and Management. 4th Ed. Elsevier. 2019.","guid":"G-_cRM1YQV6xXM0C3owx8g","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"2. Darley FL, et al. Differential Diagnostic Patterns of Dysarthria. J Speech Hear Res. 1969;12(2):246-69.","guid":"byza-tGXRji_qItLWYDMYQ","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"3. Hillis AE. Aphasia: Progress in the last quarter of a century. Neurology. 2007;69(2):200-13.","guid":"tbvVAnXKRNmWGEm3ZPOKwA","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"4. Mesulam M. Primary Progressive Aphasia. Ann Neurol. 2001;49(4):425-32.","guid":"Q6IxSZUQRx-0l7j0KhcSew","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"169","text":"5. Enderby P. Frenchay Dysarthria Assessment. Int J Lang Commun Disord. 1983;18(2):159-70.","guid":"dKTnJxvMTBavpoRqC1W5oQ","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"169","text":"6. Guía caso clínico disartria subcortical (Acevedo, 2025). Google Drive INGER.","guid":"y72j8wffSVeOy8beFZBhsQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":175,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Semiologia_Disartria_Afasia","id":"map_1451","resolved_references":[]}